          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-copy-1626261600236-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-copy-1626261600236-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-copy-1626261600236-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-copy-1626261600236-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the tortillas are warmed through, remove them from the oven and transfer them to a chopping board</p><p>Add the<strong> ciabatta slices</strong> to the tray with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and put them in the oven for 3-4 min or until crisp and lightly golden</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-copy-1626261663703-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
