            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>coronation chicken wraps</strong> with the <strong>cheesy nibbles </strong>and <strong>remaining salad</strong> to the side</p><p>Top the salad with the<strong> tomato wedges</strong> and drizzle over the <strong>dressing</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
